Supports dont have tanky items because riot nerfs them Because of other people picking up support items as if they cant just let other champions be supportive if they want to build supportive items. The other reason is because When support items have okay stats for its gold its essentally the same as tank items because riot has the same philosophy with tank items as they do support items Cheap Defensive and usually team orientated Although some tank items are more expensive they dont get more defenses for being expensive
